# 🤖 AI Sentiment Analyzer

An AI-powered Sentiment Analysis application built using Python that analyzes user-entered text and predicts whether the sentiment is **Positive**, **Negative**, or **Neutral** using Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

The AI Sentiment Analyzer helps users understand the emotional tone of text by processing sentences and classifying their sentiment. This project demonstrates the practical use of Machine Learning and NLP for text analysis.

---

## ✨ Features

- Analyze text sentiment in real-time
- Classifies text as Positive, Negative, or Neutral
- User-friendly interface
- Fast and accurate predictions
- Easy to customize and extend
- Built with Python and NLP libraries

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Python 3
- Scikit-learn
- NLTK
- Pandas
- NumPy
